@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_ccoqgv(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = (wp.sin(0.00) * wp.cos(0.42))
    v2 = wp.exp(wp.sin((v0 + 0.95 - v2 + 0.35)))
    tmp = tmp
    v1 = (wp.exp(0.23) + (v2 * (tmp + 0.21 - tmp + 0.98)))
    tmp = (wp.exp((v1 + 0.23 + v0 + 0.12)) / wp.exp((v2 + 0.71 * v2 + 0.45)))
    v2 = (wp.abs(wp.sin(v2 + 0.81)) / (0.09 * wp.sin(v1 + 0.57)))
    data[tid] = v0
